<li id="cite_note-12"><b><a href="#cite_ref-12" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFHodge.2C_Charles1871">Hodge, Charles (1871). <a href="http://www.ccel.org/ccel/hodge/theology2.iv.i.iii.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ccel.org/ccel/hodge/theology2.iv.i.iii.html" rel="nofollow">"Systematic Theology - Volume II - Infralapsarianism"</a>. Christian Classics Ethereal Library<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.ccel.org/ccel/hodge/theology2.iv.i.iii.html" class="external free" title="http://www.ccel.org/ccel/hodge/theology2.iv.i.iii.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.ccel.org/ccel/hodge/theology2.iv.i.iii.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-06-04</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Systematic+Theology+-+Volume+II+-+Infralapsarianism&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Hodge%2C+Charles&amp;rft.au=Hodge%2C+Charles&amp;rft.date=1871&amp;rft.pub=Christian+Classics+Ethereal+Library&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ccel.org%2Fccel%2Fhodge%2Ftheology2.iv.i.iii.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Calvinism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-13"><b><a href="#cite_ref-13" title="">^</a></b> See Stephen Ashby, "A Reformed Arminian View", in <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFPinson2002">Pinson, J. Matthew, editor (2002). <i>Four Views on Eternal Security</i>. Grand Rapids: Zondervan. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0310234395" class="internal">ISBN 0310234395</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Four+Views+on+Eternal+Security&amp;rft.aulast=Pinson&amp;rft.aufirst=J.+Matthew%2C+editor&amp;rft.au=Pinson%2C+J.+Matthew%2C+editor&amp;rft.date=2002&amp;rft.place=Grand+Rapids&amp;rft.pub=Zondervan&amp;rft.isbn=0310234395&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Calvinism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-14"><b><a href="#cite_ref-14" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFCollin_Hansen2006">Collin Hansen (2006-9-22). "<a href="http://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2006/september/42.32.html" class="external text" title="http://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2006/september/42.32.html" rel="nofollow">Young, Restless, Reformed</a>". <i><a href="/wiki/Christianity_Today" title="Christianity Today">Christianity Today</a></i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2006/september/42.32.html" class="external free" title="http://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2006/september/42.32.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2006/september/42.32.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2009-03-13</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Young%2C+Restless%2C+Reformed&amp;rft.jtitle=%5B%5BChristianity+Today%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=Collin+Hansen&amp;rft.au=Collin+Hansen&amp;rft.date=2006-9-22&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.christianitytoday.com%2Fct%2F2006%2Fseptember%2F42.32.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Calvinism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
